Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:23.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's going pretty well \Nwith your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is. T-To tell the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:27.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of proposing to her
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:30.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,once this business deal goes through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:32.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a reason to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:10.00,Kanojo_Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,If {\c&H53AC43&}Her {\c&H085DF0&}Flag {\c&HD2C345&}Breaks{Kanojo ga flag wo oraretara}{Z: I just simplified colors here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:14.01,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Number,EPisode Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode {\c&H8200D1&}1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:14.01,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Title,EPisode Title,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\c&H72D09E&}Going to {\c&HA159DB&}Marry Her \N{\c&H31BBEE&}Once I {\c&HEAC95C&}Leave This School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:17.01,Hatagaya_02:23,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hatagaya Academy High School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:22.14,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,BG,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Students of Hatagaya Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.68,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What happened there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.06,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it was \Njust a normal accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.11,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:37.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:39.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.08,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.83,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,He was wearing our uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.96,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,But Hatagaya Academy has classes from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.58,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,kindergarten all the way to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:52.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're all going to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,meet a new friend today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Go ahead and come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.68,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to \Nfind him that easi—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:13.98,Hatate_03:19,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate \NSouta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,She stood up and then \Nsat right back down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Was she stretching?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:29.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,So where should we have \Nour Souta-chan sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,"Chan"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,There's an open seat right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,The seat right behind Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.32,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.94,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.32,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That weird guy from this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Hotate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hatate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R1,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate-kun, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R1,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R1,0000,0000,0000,,Hotate— I mean, Hatate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:23.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R1,0000,0000,0000,,If you need something, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R1,0000,0000,0000,,Also if you want to know about any \Nof the girls, I've got your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,All the ladies like me, so I don't \Nthink I'll be needing your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R1,0000,0000,0000,,But no one likes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:41.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R2,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you be my servant. Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite the sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R2,0000,0000,0000,,Two sadists won't get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,RA/B,0000,0000,0000,,Want to join us in our quest to become \Nthe number one high school baseball team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I like soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Hotate Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You shall give me a moment of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:12.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I can't stand not solving \Nany mystery that catches my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:15.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Now you shall tell me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? T-Tell you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it glistening in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Glistening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Like fresh fish or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You keep looking above people's heads—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,right here—and then making some sort \Nof decision based on that, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You looked again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you keep worrying about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,whatever's above my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That truck from this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I know you haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You were doing something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:50.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I know that's why all of that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it was, \Nbut I'm certain you did something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You see something, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So you were at that intersection...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:04.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There was this fly—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to fool me with that rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Now tell me what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about "flags"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:18.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can actually see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,These flags, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Not just see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I instinctively know what I have \Nto do to destroy those flags,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That business deal is \Nnever going to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:40.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I destroyed the "death flag" \Nthat was waving above his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So did you do the same thing \Nin the classroom, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,With that guy who was talking\Nabout helping you with girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I shattered his "friendship flag."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And that girl who was coming on to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That was her "romance flag."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Give those bad gags of yours a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the death flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but why destroy those \Nfriendship and romance flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:19.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be a hero, who \Ndoesn't use his powers for his own good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you said was \Njust a bad joke, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you because \NI wanted you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Misfortune comes to people \Nwho get too close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:35.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,see people get hurt any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.00,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,don't involve yourself with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't matter \Nto you if I'm a loner or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about being \Nalone so trivially!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:10.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you're just rejecting \Nanyone who approaches you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about the \NPremium Ambriel disaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The luxury liner that sank \Nthe other day? What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,All of the passengers \Nare missing, except one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Only a single person was rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.54,truth_08:33,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The truth behind the Premium Ambriel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.42,rescued_08:35,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta: the lone survivor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to tell you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your double-talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta(BG),0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My eyes! My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of those eyes of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:36.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of your \Nobsession with your own misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:44.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you making me \Nremember things I don't want to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Misfortune comes to people \Nwho get too close to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your talk about being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,How about taking a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a "flag" above my head, \Nlike the ones you've mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:55.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there isn't anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:00.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel any love or friendship \Ntowards you in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And as such, I shouldn't have \Nany of those flags of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Even I did, that \Noverly self-defeating
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,attitude of yours would \Ndestroy it in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't like something about \Nyou, I'm going to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and when I want to yell \Nat you, I'm going to yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You should just do the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,In short...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop looking so \Ndepressed in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami Knight Bladefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I hate being called by my \Nlast name. Use my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You add "-san" or "-chan," \Nand you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me "Souta."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,By all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.30,Hatagaya_02:23,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Hatagaya Academy High School
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.83,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A friendship flag, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Mahougasawa Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mahougasawa Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Maho...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mahougasawa-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Akane's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Mahougasawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Akane's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need something, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time a boy's said \Nmy name without an honorific!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Does she have a flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Could I eat lunch with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:56.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,He said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You broke her flag, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't really thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I won't bug you at all, \Nso we can eat together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't break her flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The flag's there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Can I eat with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, I really don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll just start eating until \Nyou really think I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I want to \Neat with a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just wait until you \Nfinish eating, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:36.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Knock yourself out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,She shattered your flag instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch, lunch! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this girl, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard of \Nthe Mahougasawa Group?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,She's the heir to the owner of the whole group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So one of those \Nsuper-rich girls, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:55.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Nanami-chan's a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,She's the 13th princess of the \NPrincipality of Bladefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I might be a princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm the princess of a small \Nbackwater country in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We've got 10 princes and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,14 princesses in a small castle, \Nso we don't really get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:19.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got sent to this \Nisland nation in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We're a poor principality,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,so it's strange I'm \Nstudying overseas here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't have any money...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I have lots of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:28.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. There's something \Nmore important than money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's our friendship, \Nsparkling like a gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth, the three of us will
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,be bound by friendship, \Na bond strong than diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,All you did is eat your lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:47.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So her flag comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and extremely quick at \Nthat. She's a toughie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,"Why," is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she doesn't brag about being \Npart of the famous Mahougasawa Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,she's got this kind, lovable \Natmosphere about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and is always surrounded by friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,In short,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,she has everything you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that has anything \Nto do with those flags you speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:20.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is someone like that \Ntrying to get close to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Try asking her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to get close to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't just leave a dog \Nsitting there getting pelted by rain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,or a cat pitiably crying out for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.28,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,So basically a pet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:50.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're basically being charitable to \Nall of the dogs and cats out there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,since you have so much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:02.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like you're screaming out for \Nhelp more than any cat or dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.13,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,So worse than a pet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:08.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, given how gloom and doom you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,you need a friend like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, you'll be \Nmy friend, won't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,can I go to your house, \Nlike friends do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. My house is a complete mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a neat-freak, \Nalthough I may not look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for me to like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane(BG),0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing me along?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're a friend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Right. So where is this \N"Quest Dorm" place, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The station after the \NHatsudai school station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The next station over is \N10 kilometers away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hatagaya Academy is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I know the place is large,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but I never would have thought \Nthis was part of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,A farming village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,It's abandoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I told you two it was a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.13,Danger_16:35,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dangerous, the sign's crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:31.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dangerous, \Nthere're holes in the stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The holes are what make it dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be surprised if the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.35,Hatagaya_02:23,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Quest Dorm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,floor on the second level \Ncollapsed at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This here's my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look much better in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:49.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just happy I have\Na place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask for much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've \Nbeen to a friend's house
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and been in a guy's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's an overstatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You have lots of friends, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:02.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:08.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to be your\Nfriend for a while now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't just leave a dog \Nsitting there getting pelted by rain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,or a cat pitiably crying out for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm basically a pet, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to see you laugh, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to laugh forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to hit the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see him laugh some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you like so \Nmuch about Souta, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I have no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand not solving any
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,mystery that catches my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I saw Souta-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:54.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,it felt like someone grabbed my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:58.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do something for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So love at first sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Love at first sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Not that. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,This story's from when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was the granddaughter of \Nthe head of the Mahougasawa Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:20.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,They sent me to a library \Nto expand my knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:24.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and that was the first time I met a \Nfriend my age, who felt like an equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:29.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,So exchanging the things we \Ncared about was just something
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:33.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,we did to show our \Nfeelings for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:37.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But to the adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,the things we shared had\N very different values.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:43.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Our "equal" relationship was shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and a wall went up that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,divided us into different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The Group called her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,"pitiable" and looked down on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't save that "pitiable girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,And so I ran into Souta-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and thought to myself, \N"I can save someone this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and if I could pull that \Noff, then I could, in turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,somehow make up for being \Npitiable myself so long ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:20.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's why these selfish \Ndesires of mine aren't love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them be love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really see a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You two are alike in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:29.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:33.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Souta said something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:37.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That people would meet misfortune if \Nthey got too close to him, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What caused you two to think like \Nthat may have been different,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but if you both aren't trying \Nto make yourselves happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and are trying to make \Neach other happy instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I think you both will
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,end up happy in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chan, you're a poet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I take that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It was a poem! A poem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I take it all back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It was a wonderful poem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying poem already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.39,Copy of Kanojo_Flag_Main_Top,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, you're so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.77,Danger_20:16,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:11.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,He said "no" again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:17.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I left something in Souta-kun's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:33.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A death flag just appeared \Nabove Akane's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't it breaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see anything that \Nwould bring this on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,tell me anything you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea \Nwhat could cause this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What did you talk to Akane about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What? You talked about her past?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:59.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,it creates death flags that are \Nfar worse than normal ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:01.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.91,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What do I need to destroy this flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.33,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship? Love? Memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Souta-kun, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:23.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I destroyed your house...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call an ambulance right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.44,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The flag's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Did that girl
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,hate me so much I fell down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:43.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she wanted to be \Nfriends with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.70,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not shattering...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're keeping that safe \Nuntil you can see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.75,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not shattering!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to see her again, \Nand become friends with her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.71,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not shattering. \NWhy isn't it shattering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This happened to you because \Nyou weren't keeping it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,you shouldn't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You should give people hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:11.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,just like you did for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to surround yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,by a lot more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and do the same for all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.74,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't working! \NIt won't shatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that once you recover from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.33,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.83,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It this a romance flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:30.79,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.12,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't shatter that one, \NI'll just make another stand in its place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.75,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A flag of life that will \Noverpower the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hate me for this, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:02.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.15,Danger_20:16,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,350)}Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:52.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:53.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.31,complete_25:05,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:59.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A "conquest complete" flag, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That was nerve-wracking,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:18.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure the next episode will have \Nme back to living my old, peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:20.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you just had that flag appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:22.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, is there anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:24.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,living in the Quest Dorm with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:24:28.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{commercial sPot #3}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:28.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Who else besides me would \Nchoose to live there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:30.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be taking one more flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:31.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be just like this next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:33.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:34.95,Kanojo_Flag_Next_Ep_Number,Titles,0000,0000,0000,,Episode {\c&HE7B731&}2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:34.95,Kanojo_Flag_Next_Ep_Title,Titles,0000,0000,0000,,Girls {\c&H63C296&}are in the {\c&H27AFEE&}Dorm. \N{\c&HD1C658&}But I {\c&HA54BE3&}can't say it yet. {\c&H58C889&}Wait until {\c&HCFBD58&}tomorrow.
